Class ClientScoreData

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--pc2.ex.ClientScoreData
public class ClientScoreData
extends java.lang.Object

Client Score/Statistics Data, per Team

Stores score and statistics data for a specific client, including rank, score, number of problems solved and time of last problem solved (as a tie breaker).
